From: Paulo Ricardo <paulo@umbler.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 13:59:03 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?fix(chat):=20conversa=20ativa=20usa=20--umb-bg-?=
 =?UTF-8?q?active=20(=C2=A722)?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

.umb-conv-item.active passa a usar var(--umb-bg-active) em vez de
var(--umb-chat-list-active). Seleção de conversa agora compartilha o
mesmo fundo sólido de qualquer outro item selecionado do DS (linha de
tabela, item de menu dropdown, card).

Patch mínimo: 1 linha de CSS alterada. Nenhuma remoção de token,
nenhuma alteração de JS.
---
 umbootstrap-design-system.html | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/umbootstrap-design-system.html b/umbootstrap-design-system.html
index 93a3b60..201c1c6 100644
--- a/umbootstrap-design-system.html
+++ b/umbootstrap-design-system.html
@@ -1627,7 +1627,7 @@
     }
     .umb-conv-item:hover { background: var(--umb-chat-list-hover); }
     .umb-conv-item.active {
-      background: var(--umb-chat-list-active);
+      background: var(--umb-bg-active);
       box-shadow: inset 3px 0 0 var(--bs-primary);
     }
     .umb-conv-avatar {
-- 
2.34.1

